snippet.title: The Water Knight
snippet.description: The Water Knight Action game. Jump from platform to plat form and try to reach the treasure of each level.

snippet.title: Angry King
snippet.description: Angry King Action game. Collect all items and stay alive timing your jumps right from platform to platform.

snippet.title: Platform Racing
snippet.description: Platform Racing Multiplayer platform action game. Try to get to the end of the level before your opponents do.

snippet.title: Platform Racing 2
snippet.description: Platform Racing 2 Online multiplayer platform game. Try to be the first person to reach the end of the level.

snippet.title: The Mechanicer
snippet.description: The Mechanicer Platform puzzle. Get the robot to the exit of each stage pulling switches, moving stuff and more.

snippet.title: Perspective
snippet.description: Perspective Platform adventure. Follow your master to solve the puzzles and change perspective to get going.

snippet.title: Formula Driver 3D
snippet.description: Formula Driver 3D Racing game. Prove your F1 skills on the different tracks and earn cash to upgrade your car.

snippet.title: Incredipede
snippet.description: Incredipede Platform adventure. You are an unevolved life-form and you must collect the food to evolve.

snippet.title: The Prince Edward
snippet.description: The Prince Edward Platform adventure. As a prince you need to prove yourself completing all of the achievements.

snippet.title: Sparkman: Stop World
snippet.description: Sparkman: Stop World Platform game. Try to collect all the dots in order to activate the exitpoint of each level.
